 Why Dynamo DB?

-- Auto scales
-- Default settings for throughput

IAM Setup for secure connections

Why AWS Lambda?
-- High throughput and scalability, using AWS Lambda is a suitable option.
-- AWS Lambda automatically scales based on the number of incoming requests, making it well-suited for handling
high-throughput workloads.

Additionally, it simplifies the deployment and scaling aspects of our backend, allowing us to focus on the application's
logic.

